# Pwani Love - Cursor Rules

## Project Context
- Dating/matchmaking app for Kenyan coast region
- Flutter mobile app + Next.js admin + Supabase backend
- Coastal, soft, modern UI/UX theme

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript for Next.js (strict mode)
- Use Dart for Flutter (null safety, best practices)
- Follow Flutter Material Design 3 guidelines
- Prefer functional components in React/Next.js

## Architecture Principles
- Keep mobile app and admin dashboard separate
- Use Supabase for all backend services
- Implement RLS policies for security
- Design for scalability (future Python microservices)

## UI/UX Guidelines
- Coastal theme: warm colors (blues, corals, soft whites)
- Smooth animations and transitions
- Mobile-first design
- Accessible and inclusive

## File Organization
- Keep related files together
- Use clear, descriptive names
- Document complex logic
- Maintain consistent structure across apps

